<div class="ArticleView">
        
        
        
        <div class="ArticleImgContent">
            <h2><a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/equality/internasjonalt_likestillingsarbeid/gender-equality----a-key-to-democracy.html?id=611080">Gender Equality - – a key to democracy</a></h2>        
                
            <p>
               
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
    



		 <div class="ArticleView">
			<div class="ArticleContent">                
				
				    <h2><a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/ethnic-discrimination/Comprehensive-protection-against-discriminiation-NOU-200914.html?id=579248">Comprehensive protection against discriminiation (NOU 2009:14)</a></h2>
				    
			</div>
		</div>
    


<div class="ArticleView">
        <img src="/upload/BLD/Ingresssbilder/menn_og_likestilling_150x113.jpg" alt="menn og likestilling
menn og likestilling" class="ArticleImg" />
        
        
        <div class="ArticleImgContent">
            <h2><a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/equality/men-and-gender-equality.html?id=1252">Men and gender equality</a></h2>        
                
            <p>
               Gender equality can only be achieved when men and women work together towards the same goals and agree that traditional masculinities and femininities have aspects that need to be changed. 
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
    


<div class="ArticleView">
        <img src="/Upload/BLD/Ingresssbilder/Likestilling_og_diskrimineringsombudet_150x113.jpg" alt="Likestilling og diskrimineringsombudet
Likestilling og diskrimineringsombudet" class="ArticleImg" />
        
        
        <div class="ArticleImgContent">
            <h2><a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/equality/gender-equality-in-norway.html?id=445721">A joint machinery against all forms of discrimination</a></h2>        
                
            <p>
               The Equality and Anti-discrimination Ombud and the Equality and Anti-discrimination Tribunal were established 1 January 2006.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
    


<div class="ArticleView">
        <img src="/Upload/BLD/Ingresssbilder/Kjonn_og_makt_150x113.jpg" alt="Kjønn og makt
Kjønn og makt" class="ArticleImg" />
        
        
        <div class="ArticleImgContent">
            <h2><a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/equality/kjonn_og_makt/Balanced-gender-representation-on-compan.html?id=1250">Balanced gender representation on company boards</a></h2>        
                
            <p>
               From 1 January 2004, the boards in all state owned companies are obliged to have a minimum of 40 percent representation of each gender. The Parliament has passed corresponding amendments regarding public limited companies in the private sector. 
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
    

