        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/aktuelt/taler_artikler/ministeren/taler-og-artikler-av-barne--likestilling/2010/Including-men-for-womens-rights-and-gender-equality.html?id=598259" title="">
                        Including men for women’s rights and gender equality
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">UN COMMISSION ON THE STATUS OF WOMEN 1 – 12 MARCH 2010 </h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, 20.03.2010]</p>
                <p> Gender equality is good business for a country.   OECD declared in 2007 that “gender equality strengthens long-term economic development”. The former European Commissioner Vladimir Spidla said that “Women are driving job growth in Europe and helping us reach our economics target”. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
