            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/press/news/2009/genderequality_fund.html?id=587005" title="">
                        Norway provides NOK 60 million to promote women’s rights
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 24.11.2009]</p>
                <p>Norway will provide NOK 40 million (USD 7 million) to UN efforts to combat female genital mutilation and violence against women in developing countries. At the same time, Norway will contribute NOK 20 million (USD 3.5 million) to the new UN Fund for Gender Equality.  </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
